            </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-primary-900">Real-World Impact</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Engage in discussions on deploying generative AI in diverse environments—from edge devices to immersive AR/VR platforms.</p>
